name: Brokenhearted
description:
She was like a river I'm like the wind. There are so many things I want to tell you. I want to have fun with you, laugh together, get drunk together, together and together. I love you so much But I have to take care of myself, and if it is possible I hope that in the future we can get back together. But now I'm heartbroken with you.

2433 × 3637 px 
Shot on 35mmfilm in BKK, Thailand 2021
